item.title: CVE-2017-18102|2024-08-05T21:13:48.168Z -- atlassian -- atlassian-renderer
item.description: The wiki markup component of atlassian-renderer from version 8.0.0 before version 8.0.22 allows remote attackers to inject arbitrary HTML or JavaScript via a cross site scripting (XSS) vulnerability in nested wiki markup.
